Home / Brief / Knutson promotes Christenson to project manager St. Louis Park-based Knutson Construction has promoted Ryan Christenson to project manager. Knutson promotes Christenson to project manager By: Brian Johnson July 31, 2015 3:25 pm 0 St. Louis Park-based Knutson Construction has promoted Ryan Christenson to project manager.
